text: Thanks @SocialMasking but the detriments materially outnumber the benefits to me on Twitter. Haters gonna hate, why should I bother giving out free analysis when I get such a pushback. Over and out.

@jimcramer Take a break from twitter. I am. Your franchise is established and impenetrable. It is too often a vile cesspool and its a waste of time defending ourselves. The sharks make it difficult to get to the good fish. Unfortunate but it is what it is.
